body:
Honestly, as stressful as the game can get, with team comps, itemization and ranked/promos, stacking champs make things much more complicated.

&#039;&#039;Instead of your usual game, we&#039;re going to give you a time limit. These 2 fellas {{champion:75}}  {{champion:45}}  will give you around 20 minutes to end the game before they become too strong for you to handle, no matter the numbers.&#039;&#039; 

God forbid you get both these cucks in one game. Depending on your play style, you&#039;re either going to have a little resistance or completely shut down. You&#039;re going to be made into their little bitch if you don&#039;t close the game before they get irreversibly strong. And good luck having any gameplay if you&#039;re squishy, i.e ADCs and most mid laners (and some junglers and top laners). Riot should just make them stack like kindred, which is why I didn&#039;t mention her in this even tho she also stacks. make it a certain amount of farm at a time and not all of it.
